[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000022_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000022_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "I am made to tread those steps thrice which I need not to have trod but once; yea, now too I am like to be lost in the night, for the day is well nigh spent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000022_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000022_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "O that I had not slept!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Words are too weak to tell the joy of Christian when he had got back his scroll.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "He laid it up in the breast of his coat and gave thanks to God.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000023_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000023_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "But, ere he got to the top, the sun went down on Christian, and he soon saw that two wild beast stood in his way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000023_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000023_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Ah, thought he, these beasts range in the night for their prey; and if they should meet with me in the dark, how should I fly from them?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000023_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000023_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "I see now the cause of all those fears that drove Mistrust and Timorous back.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Fear not the two wild beasts, for they are bound by chains, and are put here to try the faith of those that have it, and to find out those that have none.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Tell me, whence come you?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Christian.--I am come from the Town of Destruction, and am on my way to Mount Zion; but the day is far spent, and I would, with your leave, pass the night here.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Watchful.--What is your name?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Christian.--My name is now Christian, but at first it was Graceless.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Watchful.--How is it you came so late?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "The sun is set.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "When Watchful told her why Christian had come there, she said: What is your name?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "There, they say, is no death; and there I shall dwell with such as love the Lord.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Charity.--Have you a wife and babes?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Christian.--Yes, I have.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Charity.--And did you pray to God to put it in their hearts to go with you?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Christian.--Yes, and that with much warmth, for you may think how dear they were to me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000048_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000048_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "And they brought out the jaw bone of an ass with which Samson did such great feats, and the sling and stone with which David slew Goliath of Gath.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105815_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105815/7697_105815_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Then they told him it was Immanuel's Land.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105817_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105817/7697_105817_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Christian.--Friend, what shall we do?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105817_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105817/7697_105817_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Shall we let Giant Despair rule us?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_105817_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/105817/7697_105817_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Who knows but that God, who made the world, may cause him to die, or lose the use of his limbs as he did at first.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Therefore in the state of innocence, before man had disobeyed, nothing disobeyed him that was naturally subject to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000000_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000000_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "This can be proved in three ways.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000000_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000000_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Secondly, this is proved by the order of Divine Providence which always governs inferior things by the superior.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000000_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000000_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Therefore the subjection of other animals to man is proved to be natural.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Now an angel is naturally higher than man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Therefore certain things in regard to animals could be done by angels, which could not be done by man; for instance, the rapid gathering together of all the animals.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "But man needed animals in order to have experimental knowledge of their natures.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "This is signified by the fact that God led the animals to man, that he might give them names expressive of their respective natures.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Whether Man Had Mastership Over All Other Creatures?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Now in man reason has the position of a master and not of a subject.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "Wherefore man had no mastership over the angels in the primitive state; so when we read \"all creatures,\" we must understand the creatures which are not made to God's image.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "So in the state of innocence man had mastership over the animals by commanding them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7697_245712_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7697/245712/7697_245712_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7697",
        "content": "But of the natural powers and the body itself man is master not by commanding, but by using them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
